323
00:59:48,340 --> 00:59:50,699
[SPEAKER_01] A, Reddit, ok.

324
00:59:50,699 --> 00:59:52,119
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da, Reddit.

325
00:59:52,119 --> 00:59:59,860
[SPEAKER_01] I tamo ste zapravo komunicirali, tamo ste komunicirali svoj initial coin offering, je li tako?

326
00:59:59,860 --> 01:00:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ili ti ICO.

327
01:00:01,000 --> 01:00:02,099
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je.

328
01:00:06,099 --> 01:00:09,440
[SPEAKER_01] Ok, mislim, nevjerovatan uspjeh.

329
01:00:09,440 --> 01:00:15,400
